songs.title: I Gotta Have My Baby Back
songs.lyrics:
Baby, baby, I miss you so very much it hurts me
Baby, I just gotta, gotta have my baby back
Can't sleep, can't eat because I miss my sweet baby sweet
I just gotta, I just gotta, I gotta have my baby back

Alone in a tavern
People all around
Laughing and dancing
Paintin' the town
Jukebox is playing
Songs about you
Songs with memories making me blue

Baby, come on home
Without my baby I just couldn't go on
I just gotta, I just gotta
I gotta have my baby back
